text: Liuba Dragomir (born 6 May 1985) is a Moldovan former footballer who played as a midfielder. She has been a member of the Moldova women's national team. ==International career== Dragomir capped for Moldova at senior level during the 2007 FIFA Women's World Cup qualification (UEFA second category). ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Moldova women's international footballers
